Here's the PlantUML component diagram for the `ingeniala_heybluekata` repository:

```plantuml
@startuml ingeniala_heybluekata

package "HeyBlue System" {
    [User Management] as UserMgmt
    [Interaction & Gamification] as Gamification
    [Commerce] as Commerce
    [Content Management] as ContentMgmt
    [Data Archiving & Analytics] as Analytics
    [Notification & Messaging] as Notifications
    [Security Layer] as Security

    component "API Gateway" as ApiGateway {
        [Omnichannel BFF]
        [HeyBlue BFF Mobile]
        [BFF Web Container]
    }

    component "AWS Services" as Aws {
        [Cognito]
        [DynamoDB]
        [S3]
        [CloudFront]
        [Kinesis]
        [Lambda]
        [Athena]
        [Glacier]
    }
}

UserMgmt --> Cognito : uses
UserMgmt --> DynamoDB : stores data
Gamification --> DynamoDB : stores data
Commerce --> DynamoDB : stores data
ContentMgmt --> S3 : stores
ContentMgmt --> CloudFront : delivers
Analytics --> Athena : queries
Analytics --> Glacier : archives
Notifications --> Kinesis : processes events

ApiGateway --> UserMgmt : calls
ApiGateway --> Gamification : calls
ApiGateway --> Commerce : calls
ApiGateway --> ContentMgmt : calls

Security --> UserMgmt : protects
Security --> ApiGateway : secures
Security --> Aws : enforces policies

[Web Client] --> ApiGateway
[Mobile Client] --> ApiGateway

@enduml
```